room_title: Escape room "Pharaoh’s Tomb" by The Perfect Escape in Dallas-Fort Worth
room_description: You and a group of friends have finally taken that trip to Cairo, Egypt. During one of the tours of the pyramids, you all have decided to split off and explore some of the areas yourselves. Unbeknownst, stumbling across a tomb that has been undiscovered, only to find a spirit of an evil pharaoh waiting inside…
